[Pleasant music]

6
00:00:53.011 --> 00:00:59.350
â™ª You get me each night â™ª

7
00:01:01.227 --> 00:01:03.188
[Foot steps]

8
00:01:03.646 --> 00:01:11.112
[Pleasant music]

9
00:01:13.740 --> 00:01:15.742
[Traffic sounds]

10
00:01:16.993 --> 00:01:18.995
[Pleasant music]

11
00:01:31.633 --> 00:01:32.759
You ran again?

12
00:01:33.176 --> 00:01:34.719
-It's raining though.
-Yes.

13
00:01:36.638 --> 00:01:40.016
How much will God test you?

14
00:01:40.266 --> 00:01:41.726
Do you know what it means?

15
00:01:43.019 --> 00:01:44.354
Good times lie ahead.

16
00:01:44.479 --> 00:01:46.189
This is your zodiac year!

17
00:01:46.397 --> 00:01:47.690
Heard today's your last day.

18
00:01:48.108 --> 00:01:49.484
Don't work too hard.

19
00:01:49.776 --> 00:01:51.402
Just keep your life balanced.

20
00:01:53.279 --> 00:01:54.906
-So long.
-Bye.

21
00:01:55.281 --> 00:01:57.200
-Take care.
-You too.

22
00:02:06.876 --> 00:02:09.087
MIN from SUNG's Gym won today.

23
00:02:09.212 --> 00:02:10.964
He's got a strong punch.

24
00:02:11.172 --> 00:02:13.216
Yes. he proved himself.

25
00:02:13.341 --> 00:02:17.679
It seems there's no rival
for him here in Korea.

26
00:02:17.846 --> 00:02:21.182
I wonder whom he will fight next.

27
00:02:22.141 --> 00:02:23.143
I'm on time. ain't I?

28
00:02:24.227 --> 00:02:27.313
Sweet jelly and two tangerines for you.

29
00:02:28.773 --> 00:02:29.691
This is for me!

30
00:02:30.233 --> 00:02:34.487
And your favorite rolls.

31
00:02:35.446 --> 00:02:38.825
I even brought Soju that I made myself.

32
00:02:42.203 --> 00:02:44.747
I can see you're really impressed.

33
00:02:46.416 --> 00:02:47.041
Who are you?

34
00:02:47.625 --> 00:02:50.003
Who are you? Where's grandpa?

35
00:02:51.462 --> 00:02:52.881
He quit today.

36
00:02:55.258 --> 00:02:56.676
Then why did you take all this?

37
00:02:58.261 --> 00:02:59.137
You gave them to me.

38
00:03:03.141 --> 00:03:06.936
I used to watch TV shows
with him over snacks.

39
00:03:08.021 --> 00:03:09.689
Is he sick?

40
00:03:10.523 --> 00:03:11.816
Heard he's moving to another city.

41
00:03:12.901 --> 00:03:13.443
I see.

42
00:03:15.403 --> 00:03:16.905
Sorry to disturb.

43
00:03:26.122 --> 00:03:28.124
[Raindrops]

44
00:03:35.673 --> 00:03:39.260
Hey...stay for a program.

45
00:03:40.094 --> 00:03:41.262
It's pouring.

46
00:03:47.227 --> 00:03:49.270
-That color. grey!
-This is the one!

47
00:03:50.021 --> 00:03:51.022
Don't wear it.

48
00:03:51.522 --> 00:03:53.650
I've told you so many times I hate grey.

49
00:03:53.775 --> 00:03:54.567
Do you get it?

50
00:03:54.984 --> 00:03:56.069
You know why?

51
00:03:56.486 --> 00:03:58.154
This colour creates jinx.

52
00:03:58.947 --> 00:04:00.990
Do you know what I want?

53
00:04:02.367 --> 00:04:03.201
Do you?

54
00:04:04.744 --> 00:04:06.537
Wear colourful clothes.

55
00:04:07.247 --> 00:04:07.956
Do you get it?

56
00:04:08.873 --> 00:04:12.877
Promise that you will
wear colourful clothes?

57
00:04:13.127 --> 00:04:14.379
You will not wear grey colour.

58
00:04:14.879 --> 00:04:16.631
Say that you promise.

59
00:04:17.548 --> 00:04:18.591
Promise me.

60
00:04:20.426 --> 00:04:20.802
Good.

61
00:04:22.637 --> 00:04:24.639
[Pleasant music]

62
00:04:41.698 --> 00:04:43.324
Thank you for letting me watch the drama!

63
00:04:44.993 --> 00:04:47.286
Well. eat them they are very tasty.

64
00:04:49.747 --> 00:04:51.165
Do they look bad?

65
00:04:58.673 --> 00:05:00.300
And you see that pot of jasmine?

66
00:05:00.341 --> 00:05:01.843
Remember to water that once a week!

67
00:05:02.385 --> 00:05:03.428
It's very important.

68
00:05:11.060 --> 00:05:13.062
[Foot steps]

69
00:05:35.710 --> 00:05:37.170
How can I help you?

70
00:05:37.754 --> 00:05:38.087
Hello?

71
00:05:39.172 --> 00:05:40.798
Telephone number for SUNG's Gym.

72
00:05:48.014 --> 00:05:48.598
[Gasps]

73
00:05:56.898 --> 00:05:58.900
[Dramatic music]

74
00:06:20.088 --> 00:06:21.422
See you tonight.

75
00:06:23.341 --> 00:06:25.426
Yes. you can come here.

76
00:06:25.593 --> 00:06:28.471
No. you'll get all the services.

77
00:06:30.348 --> 00:06:34.435
There can be extra
charges for the visit. sir.

78
00:06:34.435 --> 00:06:36.854
I've been waiting for hours!
You only talk about extra charges?

79
00:06:36.854 --> 00:06:40.274
Sorry for the inconvenience.

80
00:06:40.441 --> 00:06:41.776
There must've been mistakes.

81
00:06:41.943 --> 00:06:44.028
Will put you to speed service.

82
00:06:48.574 --> 00:06:50.743
How about 5PM today?

83
00:06:50.743 --> 00:06:51.702
You'd better be right this time!

84
00:06:51.869 --> 00:06:53.287
I made tons of calls for this!

85
00:06:53.454 --> 00:06:55.456
I apologize once again.

86
00:06:55.498 --> 00:06:55.998
You--

87
00:06:57.416 --> 00:06:59.627
-Hello. sir.
-Did you listen how he yelled?

88
00:06:59.669 --> 00:07:01.003
I'm not her mother.

89
00:07:01.045 --> 00:07:03.089
You work at a royalty company.

90
00:07:03.131 --> 00:07:05.049
Be nicer to the customer.

91
00:07:07.176 --> 00:07:08.803
Must be tired working night shift.

92
00:07:09.762 --> 00:07:12.223
I can sleep in. It's better.

93
00:07:13.724 --> 00:07:17.603
You know you're the candidate
...for employee of the month?

94
00:07:18.563 --> 00:07:19.147
Yes. sir.

95
00:07:31.909 --> 00:07:33.452
Keep your arms down.

96
00:07:35.121 --> 00:07:37.957
Keep your guard up
even when you kick!

97
00:07:39.041 --> 00:07:42.670
Keep punching your
opponent when you go back!

98
00:07:43.421 --> 00:07:45.631
Too many things to correct.

99
00:07:46.591 --> 00:07:48.092
I can be better than you!

100
00:07:51.220 --> 00:07:54.724
Boss! Look who's here.

101
00:08:07.945 --> 00:08:09.864
I'm here to apologize. Boss.

102
00:08:11.282 --> 00:08:12.492
Please forgive me. boss.

103
00:08:13.534 --> 00:08:18.122
Take this drink and smile. will ya?

104
00:08:18.789 --> 00:08:22.627
You are a big man
so get over with the past!

105
00:08:24.795 --> 00:08:25.880
Forget the past?

106
00:08:26.172 --> 00:08:30.301
I even couldn't feed
my own sons properly...

107
00:08:30.843 --> 00:08:33.054
...as I gave everything to him!

108
00:08:35.890 --> 00:08:37.266
Damn cheater!

109
00:08:44.649 --> 00:08:47.777
It's just his kids didn't like eating.

110
00:08:52.782 --> 00:08:56.452
Attention! Look who's here.

111
00:08:56.869 --> 00:08:58.037
JANG Chul-min.

112
00:08:58.246 --> 00:09:00.873
National champion in '99.

113
00:09:01.290 --> 00:09:02.667
He swept all game.

114
00:09:02.959 --> 00:09:05.962
All won by KOs with a few punches.

115
00:09:06.003 --> 00:09:08.005
He anhiliated his opponents.

116
00:09:08.172 --> 00:09:11.676
And I got beat up by him at the final.

117
00:09:13.886 --> 00:09:14.804
It's been a while.

118
00:09:15.680 --> 00:09:18.599
Right. I forgot that.

119
00:09:19.308 --> 00:09:20.434
But Chul-min. remember.

120
00:09:20.559 --> 00:09:24.188
He's not the same guy who you blew away.

121
00:09:24.438 --> 00:09:28.025
He's the best mixed martial arts player.

122
00:09:28.484 --> 00:09:30.987
He'll make it to UFC soon.

123
00:09:32.655 --> 00:09:34.615
I saw you on TV. You were good.

124
00:09:34.865 --> 00:09:37.285
What? Only Good?

125
00:09:39.954 --> 00:09:42.206
How about sparring
for old time's sake?

126
00:09:43.040 --> 00:09:44.083
Stop it.

127
00:09:44.125 --> 00:09:45.710
You're professional player now.

128
00:09:46.335 --> 00:09:48.504
He can't even stand for 1st round.

129
00:09:48.754 --> 00:09:49.797
Give him a break.

130
00:09:51.799 --> 00:09:52.675
-So long.
-Bye.

131
00:09:53.676 --> 00:09:54.844
Wind a bandage first.

132
00:10:00.641 --> 00:10:02.059
Just one round.

133
00:10:04.061 --> 00:10:04.770
I'm sorry. sir.

134
00:10:07.523 --> 00:10:09.525
Who let in this fool in?

135
00:10:10.443 --> 00:10:11.235
Get him out!

136
00:10:14.614 --> 00:10:15.239
Sorry. sir.

137
00:10:17.867 --> 00:10:19.869
[Foot steps]

138
00:10:28.836 --> 00:10:30.671
Do you mind opening the window?

139
00:10:31.756 --> 00:10:33.758
Sorry. I'm sensitive to smell.

140
00:10:36.761 --> 00:10:37.887
[Opens window]

141
00:10:43.768 --> 00:10:46.979
Did you work out at the gym?

142
00:10:53.027 --> 00:10:54.362
What kind of clothing have you worn?

143
00:10:56.739 --> 00:10:58.449
Plain T-shirt.

144
00:10:58.658 --> 00:11:01.744
Not you. I mean her from TV.

145
00:11:04.121 --> 00:11:04.622
Skirt.

146
00:11:04.830 --> 00:11:05.748
And the shoes?

147
00:11:06.874 --> 00:11:07.792
Yes. I have worn.

148
00:11:08.084 --> 00:11:09.627
Of course. yes.

149
00:11:09.668 --> 00:11:11.671
I mean what kind of shoes she wears.

150
00:11:15.716 --> 00:11:16.384
Woman's shoes.

151
00:11:17.885 --> 00:11:19.261
Without heel?

152
00:11:20.805 --> 00:11:21.722
And hair?

153
00:11:23.766 --> 00:11:24.725
Short and curly hair.

154
00:11:25.059 --> 00:11:25.726
Earrings?

155
00:11:25.976 --> 00:11:26.435
Yes. yes.

156
00:11:27.228 --> 00:11:29.605
Why speak too much over the program?

157
00:11:30.815 --> 00:11:32.400
'Cause I cannot see it!

158
00:11:35.403 --> 00:11:36.779
What kind of earrings?

159
00:11:41.242 --> 00:11:43.244
Similar to yours.

160
00:11:44.662 --> 00:11:45.579
Really?

161
00:11:46.664 --> 00:11:47.415
You mean it?

162
00:11:50.876 --> 00:11:52.336
[Chuckles]

163
00:12:01.137 --> 00:12:03.139
[Water tricles]

164
00:12:08.769 --> 00:12:09.228
Hey.

165
00:12:11.439 --> 00:12:12.231
Your lunch box.

166
00:12:13.899 --> 00:12:14.650
How was it?

167
00:12:15.901 --> 00:12:17.528
It was very good!

168
00:12:20.114 --> 00:12:20.990
I put some peaches.

169
00:12:21.407 --> 00:12:22.324
Did you wash them?

170
00:12:23.409 --> 00:12:23.826
Yes.

171
00:12:24.160 --> 00:12:25.453
Did you touch them a lot?

172
00:12:26.078 --> 00:12:26.495
Pardon?

173
00:12:27.455 --> 00:12:31.792
You need to eat peach
right after washing carefully.

174
00:12:32.251 --> 00:12:34.420
They get bruises and
less sweet with touching.

175
00:12:35.463 --> 00:12:36.964
Thank you for the peaches!

176
00:12:37.840 --> 00:12:38.591
By the way...

177
00:12:38.799 --> 00:12:41.093
You don't know my name.
My name is Jung-hwa

178
00:12:41.469 --> 00:12:42.386
Nice to meet you.

179
00:12:47.057 --> 00:12:49.935
You need to hold hands
when someone greets you.

180
00:13:01.238 --> 00:13:03.032
Wow. it's so hard!

181
00:13:03.282 --> 00:13:04.742
What do you do?

182
00:13:09.121 --> 00:13:10.706
Thank you for drama.

183
00:13:19.965 --> 00:13:21.967
[Foot steps]

184
00:13:25.721 --> 00:13:29.517
Family of frogs get
together on a dark night.

185
00:13:30.100 --> 00:13:34.146
They sing all night long.

186
00:13:34.271 --> 00:13:36.690
No one can listen to them.

187
00:13:38.692 --> 00:13:42.780
They don't care even
nobody's listening.

188
00:13:45.199 --> 00:13:47.409
[Water trickling]

189
00:13:53.624 --> 00:13:54.583
[Screams]

190
00:14:45.426 --> 00:14:47.428
[Pleasant music]

191
00:14:51.056 --> 00:14:53.058
[Foot steps]

192
00:15:05.362 --> 00:15:06.447
You got the new shoes?

193
00:15:08.949 --> 00:15:10.451
I can smell the new scent.

194
00:15:12.620 --> 00:15:14.330
It's been a few days.

195
00:15:16.582 --> 00:15:18.000
Drama shall start soon.

196
00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:18.876
I'll be back.

197
00:15:21.128 --> 00:15:22.546
Oh. I'm so sorry.

198
00:15:26.842 --> 00:15:29.595
Don't go! Please wait!

199
00:15:29.720 --> 00:15:31.096
I don't feel good.

200
00:15:33.974 --> 00:15:35.267
-Why are you going?
-Don't go!

201
00:15:36.977 --> 00:15:38.228
I'm here for you.

202
00:15:38.354 --> 00:15:38.729
Pardon?

203
00:15:40.564 --> 00:15:42.358
Teo says he's leaving.

204
00:15:45.277 --> 00:15:47.780
Is he crying now?

205
00:15:50.991 --> 00:15:51.492
Yes.

206
00:15:55.955 --> 00:15:58.165
He doesn't have to
go if it hurts him so bad.

207
00:16:02.127 --> 00:16:03.587
We can hear your hearts.

208
00:16:03.754 --> 00:16:06.632
Can feel better as we can't see.

209
00:16:08.634 --> 00:16:09.760
Is he handsome?

210
00:16:11.470 --> 00:16:13.013
Of course. he is an actor.

211
00:16:13.055 --> 00:16:14.390
I meant you.

212
00:16:17.810 --> 00:16:19.728
Don't bluff as I can't see.

213
00:16:23.982 --> 00:16:28.153
People say... I look manly.

214
00:16:30.990 --> 00:16:32.491
Means you are not cute.

215
00:16:51.385 --> 00:16:52.845
[Horn blaring]

216
00:16:58.017 --> 00:16:58.642
Don't touch anything!

217
00:17:14.158 --> 00:17:14.825
Are you okay?

218
00:17:18.871 --> 00:17:21.582
Oh my! All the bottles are shattered!

219
00:17:21.582 --> 00:17:22.916
What shall I do?

220
00:17:23.208 --> 00:17:24.668
I'll pay for them.

221
00:17:24.710 --> 00:17:25.586
Sorry.

222
00:17:26.086 --> 00:17:30.758
Why are you out at
night when you can't see?

223
00:17:30.924 --> 00:17:32.092
I'm so sorry.

224
00:17:32.760 --> 00:17:33.969
I'm in trouble.

225
00:17:35.512 --> 00:17:37.056
Would you please watch
the parking lot for me?

226
00:17:37.931 --> 00:17:39.683
I need to take her to the hospital.

227
00:17:40.726 --> 00:17:43.437
No problem. Go now. Take care.

228
00:17:50.235 --> 00:17:52.154
You didn't tell me your name?

229
00:17:56.325 --> 00:17:57.076
Marcelino.

230
00:17:57.201 --> 00:17:57.659
What?

231
00:18:00.621 --> 00:18:01.663
JANG Marcelino.

232
00:18:02.915 --> 00:18:04.416
You are a foreigner?

233
00:18:04.917 --> 00:18:07.169
No. I'm Korean.

234
00:18:08.086 --> 00:18:12.049
But you're Jang Marcelino?

235
00:18:12.549 --> 00:18:13.008
Yes.

236
00:18:14.885 --> 00:18:16.470
Jang Marcelino?

237
00:18:18.347 --> 00:18:18.889
Correct.

238
00:18:24.895 --> 00:18:27.898
Wait. Let's take a break.

239
00:18:31.485 --> 00:18:32.444
Can I carry you?

240
00:18:36.323 --> 00:18:37.491
You'll regret it.

241
00:18:38.659 --> 00:18:39.993
I'm fine. On my back.

242
00:18:42.204 --> 00:18:44.915
Don't complain later.

243
00:18:46.542 --> 00:18:48.710
Don't kidnap me.

244
00:19:17.155 --> 00:19:19.157
[Pleasant music]

245
00:19:31.253 --> 00:19:33.922
Hey! We're at a diversion.

246
00:19:35.090 --> 00:19:36.300
Beauty shop at the right.

247
00:19:36.300 --> 00:19:37.759
Oh! Then...

248
00:19:38.343 --> 00:19:40.137
Go straight after the right.

249
00:19:45.601 --> 00:19:47.269
I warned you.

250
00:19:49.563 --> 00:19:51.106
[Gasps]

251
00:19:55.861 --> 00:19:57.863
[Pleasant music]

252
00:20:04.661 --> 00:20:05.329
Are you okay?

253
00:20:05.370 --> 00:20:06.246
I'm fine. Totally.

254
00:20:07.331 --> 00:20:08.790
Then why am I coming down?

255
00:20:12.502 --> 00:20:14.838
And you see a kid at the corner?

256
00:20:15.339 --> 00:20:16.506
Better watch out!

257
00:20:17.090 --> 00:20:18.508
[Gasps]

258
00:20:26.975 --> 00:20:29.394
-[Agonising sigh]
-[Chuckles]

259
00:20:31.813 --> 00:20:32.940
What are you doing?

260
00:20:33.106 --> 00:20:34.024
Let's go! Let's go!

261
00:20:34.024 --> 00:20:36.151
I'll give you a shot!

262
00:20:36.401 --> 00:20:37.861
Mister. run!

263
00:20:38.779 --> 00:20:40.781
[Gasps]

264
00:20:40.989 --> 00:20:42.991
[Foot steps]

265
00:20:44.993 --> 00:20:46.328
We're here.

266
00:20:50.415 --> 00:20:51.583
You get exhausted early.

267
00:20:53.210 --> 00:20:56.380
But a man should be strong.

268
00:20:56.421 --> 00:21:01.343
There were too many
stairs. I'm out of breathe.

269
00:21:03.095 --> 00:21:06.723
Can I ask one more favor
if you have some time?

270
00:21:06.932 --> 00:21:10.018
-You must have time. no?
-Huh?

271
00:21:11.186 --> 00:21:12.437
Let me catch my breath.

272
00:21:14.272 --> 00:21:16.275
[Water trickling]

273
00:21:26.952 --> 00:21:28.161
Something's stuck in there?

274
00:21:31.289 --> 00:21:32.874
It looks like panties.

275
00:21:35.335 --> 00:21:36.461
Squirrels on it?

276
00:21:37.587 --> 00:21:39.131
-Squirrels on it.
-Give it to me.

277
00:21:41.425 --> 00:21:42.634
It was a gift.

278
00:21:42.884 --> 00:21:46.179
I've been looking all
over. Now I found it.

279
00:21:47.097 --> 00:21:48.223
-Can I have a towel. please?
-Here you are.

280
00:21:51.059 --> 00:21:53.645
What kind of music do you like?

281
00:21:56.523 --> 00:21:59.568
The music radio plays.

282
00:22:03.864 --> 00:22:07.075
It's a reward for
carrying me all the way.

283
00:22:07.534 --> 00:22:08.660
Go with your friend.

284
00:22:08.660 --> 00:22:09.661
Tickets for the concert.

285
00:22:15.709 --> 00:22:16.793
No thanks.

286
00:22:16.835 --> 00:22:18.128
I don't know music.

287
00:22:18.712 --> 00:22:20.464
Don't have anyone to go with.

288
00:22:22.090 --> 00:22:23.633
Pity you don't have friends at all.

289
00:22:24.760 --> 00:22:25.844
Want me to go with you?

290
00:22:26.970 --> 00:22:28.972
[Pleasant music]

291
00:22:29.014 --> 00:22:31.016
[Foot steps]

292
00:22:38.190 --> 00:22:40.192
[Pleasant music]

293
00:22:54.581 --> 00:22:57.084
How do you like your hair done?

294
00:22:57.417 --> 00:23:01.713
How about digital perm
which is hip in Paris

295
00:23:01.755 --> 00:23:03.715
in which the hair is curled.

296
00:23:03.799 --> 00:23:08.220
I know it will look great on you.

297
00:23:08.386 --> 00:23:09.054
You sure?

298
00:23:09.137 --> 00:23:10.347
Of course!

299
00:23:10.514 --> 00:23:13.266
How about hair from that TV drama--

300
00:23:13.350 --> 00:23:14.726
How dare you!

301
00:23:14.726 --> 00:23:16.228
So out of fashion!

302
00:23:16.228 --> 00:23:18.438
That is from some other time!
It won't work!

303
00:23:18.980 --> 00:23:20.816
Then whatever you say.

304
00:23:20.857 --> 00:23:22.776
You have a date. right?

305
00:23:23.693 --> 00:23:24.486
No.

306
00:23:24.486 --> 00:23:26.988
If you don't want to talk...

307
00:23:27.030 --> 00:23:28.740
Let's go for the digital perm.

308
00:23:34.371 --> 00:23:36.289
Should I go for the pink lipstick?

309
00:23:38.500 --> 00:23:39.709
Let's go with it.

310
00:23:49.845 --> 00:23:51.638
No. 3. No. 4...

311
00:24:25.172 --> 00:24:26.464
I hope you didn't wait long.

312
00:24:29.843 --> 00:24:37.476
Flower's in bloom in my heart.

313
00:24:38.768 --> 00:24:46.151
You're the flower.

314
00:24:47.652 --> 00:24:55.535
Petals are leading me...

315
00:24:56.620 --> 00:25:03.668
...into your arms...

316
00:25:05.629 --> 00:25:14.930
It's you who I've been waiting for.

317
00:25:15.430 --> 00:25:22.354
You don't know
how lonely I've been..

318
00:25:22.771 --> 00:25:24.522
What does female vocalist look like?

319
00:25:29.903 --> 00:25:32.948
She is a woman with big eyes

320
00:25:34.366 --> 00:25:35.700
and long hair.

321
00:25:41.957 --> 00:25:44.334
The concert really hit the spot!

322
00:25:44.834 --> 00:25:47.379
It's been so long since
I went to the concert.

323
00:25:48.755 --> 00:25:51.508
Did you get your hair done?

324
00:25:51.716 --> 00:25:53.802
You don't like it?

325
00:25:55.053 --> 00:25:55.637
I like it.

326
00:25:56.846 --> 00:25:57.597
Aren't you hungry?

327
00:25:59.099 --> 00:26:01.059
There's one place I really want to go.

328
00:26:01.434 --> 00:26:07.440
I've been there often
with the one I loved.

329
00:26:13.738 --> 00:26:14.614
Nice.

330
00:26:27.377 --> 00:26:29.045
You know Le Penseur?

331
00:26:29.504 --> 00:26:31.631
A sculpture by Rodin?

332
00:26:31.965 --> 00:26:36.761
He has really short toenails.

333
00:26:38.096 --> 00:26:40.473
I know this as I studied
sculpture at school.

334
00:26:42.309 --> 00:26:45.854
But I can't remember
things I saw everyday.

335
00:26:46.646 --> 00:26:52.277
Like flowers at our garden.
where my beauty spot is.

336
00:26:52.319 --> 00:26:55.280
...and face of my dad.

337
00:26:59.075 --> 00:27:01.036
The one I loved is my dad.

338
00:27:02.162 --> 00:27:03.997
I should've watched him carefully.

339
00:27:05.373 --> 00:27:09.169
If I remember them. I can still see them.

340
00:27:22.140 --> 00:27:23.975
I know you work at parking lot.

341
00:27:24.184 --> 00:27:25.435
And during daytime?

342
00:27:27.354 --> 00:27:30.899
I deliver water.

343
00:27:32.525 --> 00:27:34.861
What did you do when you were young?

344
00:27:36.863 --> 00:27:41.910
You lived restless
life doing bad things?

345
00:27:47.374 --> 00:27:50.293
Why do you want to know all of this?

346
00:27:56.257 --> 00:27:58.551
I can take it as you ignored me just now.

347
00:28:02.389 --> 00:28:04.349
Why can't you be honest to me?

348
00:28:05.558 --> 00:28:09.145
You know how I feel now?

349
00:28:09.187 --> 00:28:12.691
I don't know and don't care.

350
00:28:14.275 --> 00:28:16.820
But I surely know what
you ate in the morning.

351
00:28:28.790 --> 00:28:33.711
Yes. I show the people
what I eat everyday.

352
00:28:37.507 --> 00:28:38.633
Excuse me.

353
00:28:46.433 --> 00:28:47.225
[Sighs]

354
00:28:54.649 --> 00:28:57.736
Sorry you had a hard day because of me.

355
00:28:59.612 --> 00:29:03.366
Sorry for bothering you.

356
00:29:04.409 --> 00:29:05.076
Good bye.

357
00:29:09.456 --> 00:29:10.540
I'm...

358
00:29:13.793 --> 00:29:14.627
now thirty.

359
00:29:16.671 --> 00:29:17.630
I was a boxer.

360
00:29:18.757 --> 00:29:19.716
And when I was young...

361
00:29:23.094 --> 00:29:26.806
I was really a bad boy. Really.

362
00:29:29.642 --> 00:29:33.271
But now I want to be good.

363
00:29:35.023 --> 00:29:37.275
That's who I am.

364
00:29:38.693 --> 00:29:43.448
I couldn't tell you early
because I feel ashamed.

365
00:29:45.950 --> 00:29:49.204
Not because...I ignored you.

366
00:29:59.464 --> 00:30:00.423
Okay. good night.

367
00:30:08.223 --> 00:30:09.516
[Door closes]

368
00:30:10.767 --> 00:30:12.352
Okay thank you so much sir.

369
00:30:12.393 --> 00:30:14.562
Have a good day and thank you for calling.

370
00:30:23.821 --> 00:30:24.531
Yes?

371
00:30:24.989 --> 00:30:26.699
Jung-hwa. come to my cabin.

372
00:30:31.579 --> 00:30:32.455
Sit down.

373
00:30:41.673 --> 00:30:43.007
A present for you.

374
00:30:44.300 --> 00:30:45.426
Why. sir?

375
00:30:46.094 --> 00:30:49.597
Why didn't you tell me
your birthday was last week?

376
00:30:49.639 --> 00:30:52.225
You really don't have to but thank you.

377
00:30:52.308 --> 00:30:55.687
No need to thank you.
Let's have dinner next week.

378
00:30:57.897 --> 00:30:59.357
Need to get back to work.

379
00:31:08.241 --> 00:31:10.243
[Foot steps]

380
00:31:16.291 --> 00:31:18.293
[Pleasant music]

381
00:31:26.884 --> 00:31:28.886
[Car engine sounds]

382
00:31:31.139 --> 00:31:33.141
[Pleasant music]

383
00:31:46.362 --> 00:31:48.573
I hate this awkward mood.

384
00:31:49.365 --> 00:31:50.366
Hey Chul-min!

385
00:31:50.700 --> 00:31:52.577
Come back to gym.

386
00:31:52.660 --> 00:31:54.787
Boss and I need you.

387
00:31:54.954 --> 00:31:56.706
Let's start all over again.

388
00:31:59.083 --> 00:31:59.751
I'm sorry.

389
00:32:00.418 --> 00:32:01.502
I'll ask one question.

390
00:32:04.005 --> 00:32:05.131
Where have you been all these years?

391
00:32:10.637 --> 00:32:14.724
I don't know much
as I didn't learn much.

392
00:32:14.932 --> 00:32:16.643
But I know damn well
your fist is really powerful.

393
00:32:17.810 --> 00:32:19.896
Boxing is out of fashion now.

394
00:32:20.271 --> 00:32:21.814
People don't watch it.

395
00:32:22.273 --> 00:32:25.902
Asian champ earns only 3K a year.

396
00:32:26.319 --> 00:32:28.946
Let's do mixed martial arts.

397
00:32:29.656 --> 00:32:33.743
It's a shame that you
don't use that powerful fist!

398
00:32:39.457 --> 00:32:42.835
If you got nothing to say. I'm leaving.

399
00:32:44.379 --> 00:32:44.837
Boss.

400
00:32:47.757 --> 00:32:48.299
I was...

401
00:32:50.343 --> 00:32:52.512
in prison for many years.

402
00:32:53.721 --> 00:32:54.055
What?

403
00:32:56.933 --> 00:32:58.893
For 4 years and 3 months.

404
00:33:11.280 --> 00:33:13.282
[Sombre music]

405
00:33:21.833 --> 00:33:23.126
After I quit boxing...

406
00:33:23.918 --> 00:33:27.422
I beat up the people
to collect their debts.

407
00:33:27.797 --> 00:33:28.798
This was my work.

408
00:33:38.766 --> 00:33:40.768
[Gasps]

409
00:33:40.810 --> 00:33:42.812
[Foot steps]

410
00:33:58.411 --> 00:34:05.251
I sent my kids to
orphanage a long time back.

411
00:34:06.127 --> 00:34:07.628
My wife ran away.

412
00:34:11.048 --> 00:34:18.056
Your parents must've sung a
lullaby to you while you slept.

413
00:34:19.390 --> 00:34:24.145
But I can't do that...

414
00:34:25.938 --> 00:34:30.401
This is all I've got!

415
00:34:30.610 --> 00:34:31.944
Keep this too!

416
00:34:34.781 --> 00:34:39.660
Nobody sang a... damn lullaby to me.

417
00:34:43.873 --> 00:34:46.667
I'm an orphan too!

418
00:34:46.709 --> 00:34:47.543
[Door knocks]

419
00:34:48.044 --> 00:34:49.378
Hey. open the door!

420
00:34:49.796 --> 00:34:51.005
-Who the hell?
-[Door knocks]

421
00:35:05.520 --> 00:35:06.854
Brother Marcelino?

422
00:35:08.773 --> 00:35:10.108
Why are you so sad?

423
00:35:10.149 --> 00:35:12.318
You you look much nicer when you smile.

424
00:35:13.694 --> 00:35:15.738
You see?

425
00:35:15.738 --> 00:35:17.281
You have to keep that smile.

426
00:35:18.991 --> 00:35:24.205
Can't we change our
christian surname. Sister?

427
00:35:25.331 --> 00:35:25.998
Why so?

428
00:35:26.916 --> 00:35:28.417
Sounds like an actor!

429
00:35:29.252 --> 00:35:31.379
JANG Marcelino!

430
00:35:32.255 --> 00:35:34.715
I like your surname.

431
00:35:39.929 --> 00:35:42.223
We've made such
gifts after giving orders.

432
00:35:44.475 --> 00:35:46.143
Give it to your girlfriend.

433
00:36:03.578 --> 00:36:04.203
Who is it?

434
00:36:05.705 --> 00:36:07.248
So you're living here?

435
00:36:07.748 --> 00:36:08.791
Sir you?

436
00:36:09.166 --> 00:36:11.210
Why did you lie?

437
00:36:12.920 --> 00:36:16.299
You don't have any plan after work.

438
00:36:17.717 --> 00:36:19.051
Let's have tea together.

439
00:36:23.556 --> 00:36:24.557
[Sighs]

440
00:36:30.897 --> 00:36:32.815
Sorry there's no hot tea.

441
00:36:33.399 --> 00:36:34.775
I can't use the stove.

442
00:36:35.568 --> 00:36:40.281
Sorry I couldn't think that.

443
00:36:44.285 --> 00:36:46.579
Aren't you scared to live alone?

444
00:36:53.085 --> 00:36:54.754
Was it during the college?

445
00:36:55.713 --> 00:36:56.547
That accident?

446
00:36:59.342 --> 00:37:00.635
I'm so sorry.

447
00:37:01.385 --> 00:37:03.221
Sure boys went crazy for you.

448
00:37:05.348 --> 00:37:08.643
Sir please leave now.

449
00:37:09.894 --> 00:37:11.771
Does your wife know what you're doing?

450
00:37:17.026 --> 00:37:21.989
You didn't even open the present.

451
00:37:25.034 --> 00:37:29.664
Do you know. I got divorced recently

452
00:37:31.207 --> 00:37:32.875
for beating up my wife.

453
00:37:36.545 --> 00:37:38.047
I knew it.

454
00:37:39.090 --> 00:37:40.925
It really looks good on you!

455
00:37:41.384 --> 00:37:44.553
You don't know how pretty you are.

456
00:37:51.102 --> 00:37:51.686
Damn!

457
00:37:52.103 --> 00:37:52.937
God damn it.

458
00:37:54.939 --> 00:37:56.691
I'm not here for one time sex.

459
00:37:56.732 --> 00:37:59.318
I can buy much prettier girls for that.

460
00:38:00.236 --> 00:38:04.156
You need to know how I feel about you.

461
00:38:05.366 --> 00:38:06.575
Don't you understand.

462
00:38:06.617 --> 00:38:08.119
[Low pitched buzz]

463
00:38:09.870 --> 00:38:11.998
Want me to rape you?

464
00:38:11.998 --> 00:38:13.040
That's what you want?

465
00:38:14.291 --> 00:38:17.086
Please stop! Please let me go!

466
00:38:17.837 --> 00:38:19.005
Stop right now!

467
00:38:19.797 --> 00:38:21.799
[Gasps]

468
00:38:22.049 --> 00:38:25.469
[Sobbing]

469
00:38:34.645 --> 00:38:35.479
Please stop.

470
00:38:36.647 --> 00:38:40.318
Well... I work with Jung-hwa.

471
00:38:40.568 --> 00:38:41.819
I'm here to just to have tea.

472
00:38:54.331 --> 00:38:55.833
Please let him go!

473
00:38:58.335 --> 00:39:00.087
[Quivers]

474
00:39:00.588 --> 00:39:01.797
Let him go!

475
00:39:06.844 --> 00:39:08.387
Look me in the eyes.

476
00:39:10.848 --> 00:39:14.518
I'll kill you if I see you again closeby.

477
00:39:18.064 --> 00:39:20.066
[Quivers]

478
00:39:36.415 --> 00:39:36.999
Jung-hwa.

479
00:39:38.751 --> 00:39:39.460
Are you okay?

480
00:39:43.881 --> 00:39:44.924
Why did you do that?

481
00:39:47.385 --> 00:39:48.677
Do you know what will happen?

482
00:39:50.471 --> 00:39:51.972
He will fire me from the job.

483
00:39:51.972 --> 00:39:54.850
Do you still want that job?

484
00:39:56.143 --> 00:39:58.896
You should go to the police and complain.

485
00:39:58.896 --> 00:40:00.356
Because I need to survive!

486
00:40:02.525 --> 00:40:03.859
I have to live.

487
00:40:04.735 --> 00:40:07.655
I'll take care of you. I will.

488
00:40:07.780 --> 00:40:09.323
You'll get the new job for me?

489
00:40:09.573 --> 00:40:13.202
Or you'll come to
rescue whenever it happens?

490
00:40:16.705 --> 00:40:18.582
What do you think you are?

491
00:40:23.420 --> 00:40:26.048
I'll stay with you foreever.

492
00:40:28.551 --> 00:40:32.138
You're making me more helpless.

493
00:40:33.764 --> 00:40:34.473
Right?

494
00:40:48.779 --> 00:40:49.822
Please leave now.

495
00:41:10.843 --> 00:41:12.845
[Sombre music]

496
00:42:33.384 --> 00:42:34.218
[Door chimes]

497
00:42:46.146 --> 00:42:46.855
When did you come?

498
00:42:51.360 --> 00:42:52.236
A while ago.

499
00:42:55.114 --> 00:42:56.240
I quit.

500
00:42:58.033 --> 00:43:01.495
I feel so cramped inside.

501
00:43:02.955 --> 00:43:07.084
Will you take me out this weekend?

502
00:43:10.212 --> 00:43:11.714
You're not answering?

503
00:43:12.423 --> 00:43:13.924
You said you will take care of me.

504
00:43:14.592 --> 00:43:16.468
Then you can do that at least. Right?

505
00:43:18.679 --> 00:43:19.096
Yes...

506
00:43:20.514 --> 00:43:21.557
I will.

507
00:43:45.914 --> 00:43:46.415
Take this.

508
00:43:51.170 --> 00:43:52.087
What is it?

509
00:43:53.088 --> 00:43:56.091
He'll keep you company.

510
00:43:56.425 --> 00:43:58.302
He will be the eye dog when he grows up.

511
00:43:58.844 --> 00:44:00.095
Is he a Golden Retriever?

512
00:44:00.596 --> 00:44:01.138
Yes.

513
00:44:02.181 --> 00:44:03.307
Hey wow!

514
00:44:06.894 --> 00:44:08.145
What shall we call him?

515
00:44:09.063 --> 00:44:10.314
How about Easy?

516
00:44:10.606 --> 00:44:11.106
Easy?

517
00:44:11.190 --> 00:44:13.525
To live in easy.

518
00:44:15.819 --> 00:44:18.489
Then he's Jang Easy?

519
00:44:19.323 --> 00:44:22.368
Nice to meet you. Easy!

520
00:44:24.578 --> 00:44:26.580
[Pleasant music]

521
00:44:39.218 --> 00:44:44.056
I grew up in the
orphanage across this river.

522
00:44:45.182 --> 00:44:48.060
We swam and did fishing here.

523
00:44:51.063 --> 00:44:54.608
Now orphanage is flooded.

524
00:44:56.068 --> 00:45:01.365
The only place I remember is under water.

525
00:45:04.368 --> 00:45:08.163
Listen. get two pebbles for me.

526
00:45:09.248 --> 00:45:11.250
[Pleasant music]

527
00:45:18.465 --> 00:45:21.427
This pebble feels exactly like you.

528
00:45:22.553 --> 00:45:25.389
I'll carry it always thinking about you.

529
00:45:25.889 --> 00:45:29.726
And one stone with you thinking about me.

530
00:45:39.445 --> 00:45:40.821
Your hands are so warm.

531
00:45:44.700 --> 00:45:46.702
[Pleasant music]

532
00:45:53.417 --> 00:45:57.546
There must be a reason to come back now.

533
00:45:58.172 --> 00:46:00.215
He wants to earn the money.

534
00:46:00.215 --> 00:46:01.800
What's wrong with that?

535
00:46:01.842 --> 00:46:02.968
[Chuckles]

536
00:46:04.052 --> 00:46:06.889
Let's make it to UFC!

537
00:46:07.890 --> 00:46:08.557
America!

538
00:46:08.932 --> 00:46:10.934
[Up beat music]

539
00:46:11.310 --> 00:46:13.312
[Gasps]

540
00:46:17.441 --> 00:46:19.443
[Up beat music]

541
00:46:23.822 --> 00:46:24.406
[Opens door]

542
00:46:40.464 --> 00:46:42.466
[Up beat music]

543
00:46:51.475 --> 00:46:52.726
Want to read it. Easy?

544
00:46:53.185 --> 00:46:55.187
[Up beat music]

545
00:46:57.898 --> 00:46:59.900
[Screaming]

546
00:47:05.489 --> 00:47:07.115
Come in harder.

547
00:47:08.784 --> 00:47:09.743
Practice!

548
00:47:10.911 --> 00:47:13.038
1.2.3.4. 1.2.3.

549
00:47:13.455 --> 00:47:14.623
1.2.3.

550
00:47:14.915 --> 00:47:16.458
1.2.3.

551
00:47:17.209 --> 00:47:19.211
[Pleasant music]

552
00:47:22.256 --> 00:47:24.258
[Sawing sounds]

553
00:47:34.935 --> 00:47:36.270
Table on your right.

554
00:47:37.980 --> 00:47:39.273
You even rounded the corners?

555
00:47:40.315 --> 00:47:41.858
Moved furnitures a bit.

556
00:47:49.741 --> 00:47:52.286
Door mat is gone. too.

557
00:47:56.832 --> 00:47:57.708
There's a bed.

558
00:48:10.762 --> 00:48:13.849
I got the new window
to let the sun rays in.

559
00:48:29.573 --> 00:48:29.907
Why?

560
00:48:30.282 --> 00:48:31.617
I want to see you.

561
00:48:33.368 --> 00:48:35.370
[Pleasant music]

562
00:49:10.197 --> 00:49:15.118
This way I can feel and see you.

563
00:49:19.581 --> 00:49:23.210
Are you looking in my eyes?

564
00:49:25.045 --> 00:49:25.420
Yes.

565
00:49:25.754 --> 00:49:26.755
You're lying.

566
00:49:31.969 --> 00:49:33.971
[Pleasant music]

567
00:49:48.610 --> 00:49:50.612
[Pleasant music]

568
00:50:04.751 --> 00:50:06.753
[Pleasant music continues]

569
00:50:15.387 --> 00:50:17.806
-Yes!
-Very good!

570
00:50:18.557 --> 00:50:19.808
Defeat him!

571
00:50:20.350 --> 00:50:23.395
That's great! This is going to be fun!

572
00:50:26.273 --> 00:50:27.774
-Good job!
-Yay!

573
00:50:28.358 --> 00:50:29.818
Great going!

574
00:50:32.279 --> 00:50:33.780
Look at the trickery!

575
00:50:34.448 --> 00:50:36.533
We'll see during the fights.

576
00:50:36.867 --> 00:50:38.160
Come get me!

577
00:50:38.410 --> 00:50:40.871
Barking dogs seldom bite.

578
00:50:41.496 --> 00:50:42.330
Hey!

579
00:50:42.664 --> 00:50:43.373
What is this!

580
00:50:45.167 --> 00:50:47.169
[Pleasant music]

581
00:50:56.762 --> 00:50:57.846
Very good!

582
00:51:05.061 --> 00:51:05.604
[Gasps]

583
00:51:06.521 --> 00:51:08.523
[Pleasant music]

584
00:51:21.369 --> 00:51:22.829
I'm not a good dancer.

585
00:51:23.497 --> 00:51:24.039
I know.

586
00:51:25.874 --> 00:51:27.876
[Dramatic music]

587
00:51:28.335 --> 00:51:30.337
[Screaming]

588
00:51:34.257 --> 00:51:36.259
[Pleasant music]

589
00:51:46.103 --> 00:51:47.729
[Chuckles]

590
00:51:48.772 --> 00:51:50.774
[Pleasant music]

591
00:52:06.957 --> 00:52:08.750
I used to like the rains.

592
00:52:09.960 --> 00:52:12.254
But now I hate it.

593
00:52:14.047 --> 00:52:14.422
Why?

594
00:52:16.758 --> 00:52:17.300
No reason.

595
00:52:20.178 --> 00:52:20.971
Turn around.

596
00:52:21.721 --> 00:52:22.139
Why?

597
00:52:22.222 --> 00:52:23.056
Just turn around!

598
00:52:24.641 --> 00:52:27.018
What are you trying now?

599
00:52:30.981 --> 00:52:35.277
After pressing the muscle
near backbone with a thumb...

600
00:52:35.902 --> 00:52:36.736
[Yells]

601
00:52:37.487 --> 00:52:38.071
Does it hurt?

602
00:52:38.488 --> 00:52:40.907
No. It feels very good.

603
00:52:57.340 --> 00:52:59.009
What does this mean?

604
00:52:59.676 --> 00:53:00.719
The line on notebook?

605
00:53:01.136 --> 00:53:03.722
You want to learn this language?

606
00:53:04.055 --> 00:53:05.807
Just curious.

607
00:53:06.182 --> 00:53:08.435
It's a line from 'Romeo & Juliet.'

608
00:53:09.561 --> 00:53:12.314
When she talks to me with her eyes.

609
00:53:13.440 --> 00:53:16.359
I will answer her eyes.

610
00:53:19.988 --> 00:53:21.489
Why learn massage?

611
00:53:22.073 --> 00:53:23.825
Well...You never know.

612
00:53:23.867 --> 00:53:25.327
Maybe I learned it for you.

613
00:53:26.870 --> 00:53:29.039
Be sure not to get hurt.

614
00:53:29.247 --> 00:53:31.583
I sense your face gets swollen often.

615
00:53:32.542 --> 00:53:34.502
Don't worry about it.

616
00:53:34.711 --> 00:53:37.714
Do you want to open your workshop?

617
00:53:38.006 --> 00:53:40.800
You can make plates and vases...

618
00:53:41.760 --> 00:53:42.802
I'll do the delivery!

619
00:53:45.680 --> 00:53:47.682
Now tell me is the idea good.

620
00:53:56.233 --> 00:53:58.235
[Pleasant music]

621
00:54:22.050 --> 00:54:24.177
Let go with armlock. trust yourself!

622
00:54:24.219 --> 00:54:25.929
Go for it.

623
00:54:26.221 --> 00:54:27.639
You can do it.

624
00:54:28.723 --> 00:54:30.809
Very good! Yeah!

625
00:54:34.854 --> 00:54:36.356
I have placed a bet on you.

626
00:54:37.774 --> 00:54:39.734
Move forward.

627
00:54:40.235 --> 00:54:40.777
Forward.

628
00:54:42.028 --> 00:54:43.571
Very good!

629
00:54:43.655 --> 00:54:46.741
-Hit him!
-What is he doing?

630
00:54:47.117 --> 00:54:49.911
Finish him in one punch.

631
00:54:51.997 --> 00:54:53.039
What the hell!

632
00:55:04.634 --> 00:55:06.511
Break! Break!

633
00:55:06.761 --> 00:55:08.763
[Cheering]

634
00:55:13.143 --> 00:55:14.394
-Very good!
-Great!

635
00:55:14.644 --> 00:55:16.229
-You accomplished it.
-That was great!

636
00:55:16.688 --> 00:55:18.231
-You did good!
-You did good!

637
00:55:18.398 --> 00:55:20.483
-You were so good!
-Make way.

638
00:55:20.525 --> 00:55:22.360
Thank you. sir.

639
00:55:22.360 --> 00:55:24.779
You were so good!

640
00:55:25.530 --> 00:55:27.824
They added $100 more to original $300.

641
00:55:27.991 --> 00:55:29.826
Also we got some tips!

642
00:55:30.076 --> 00:55:33.580
Hey. are you still okay!

643
00:55:36.374 --> 00:55:39.627
Come to the official league and fight me.

644
00:55:40.336 --> 00:55:43.506
Ours will be a great
fight. What do you think?

645
00:55:43.840 --> 00:55:46.468
Long time no see?

646
00:55:47.260 --> 00:55:50.305
I'm not your bro. Don't take my name.

647
00:55:50.805 --> 00:55:53.308
We don't share the blood.

648
00:55:53.808 --> 00:55:57.562
You could've come out
with me leaving thay gym.

649
00:55:57.771 --> 00:55:58.730
Get lost!

650
00:56:01.066 --> 00:56:02.108
Let's go.

651
00:56:03.109 --> 00:56:04.444
See you soon in the ring.

652
00:56:07.155 --> 00:56:11.409
That son of a dog left
us for the big money.

653
00:56:11.868 --> 00:56:13.286
He couldn't pay his rent.

654
00:56:13.453 --> 00:56:15.371
Now he's driving expensive cars.

655
00:56:16.915 --> 00:56:19.751
Bro. please cut here.

656
00:56:20.835 --> 00:56:22.587
The swelling will ease up.

657
00:56:24.506 --> 00:56:25.298
She'll kill me.

658
00:56:25.757 --> 00:56:28.134
But I'm happy that you're happy.

659
00:56:28.510 --> 00:56:30.595
Let this smile always stay on your face.

660
00:56:33.681 --> 00:56:34.641
Here it goes.

661
00:56:34.724 --> 00:56:35.266
Will you be able to?

662
00:56:35.683 --> 00:56:37.393
Come on. it's not the first time.

663
00:56:37.435 --> 00:56:38.436
Just easy.

664
00:56:41.439 --> 00:56:46.569
You've hurt people so
you deserve to be hurt.

665
00:56:46.653 --> 00:56:48.655
Don't worry! Everything will be okay!

666
00:56:53.910 --> 00:56:55.954
Yes. blood is coming.

667
00:56:57.038 --> 00:56:59.457
But you just can't
stop smiling. can you?

668
00:57:01.167 --> 00:57:01.876
Very good!

669
00:57:03.044 --> 00:57:03.795
[Door closes]

670
00:57:07.006 --> 00:57:07.632
I'm home.

671
00:57:08.007 --> 00:57:10.093
How was the fight? Let me see.

672
00:57:18.184 --> 00:57:19.352
You aren't hurt a lot.

673
00:57:23.022 --> 00:57:24.691
Going somewhere?

674
00:57:25.024 --> 00:57:26.818
Tomorrow's holiday.

675
00:57:27.193 --> 00:57:29.237
So was wondering if we could go out.

676
00:57:44.961 --> 00:57:49.465
I wanted you to meet my mom and dad.

677
00:57:53.678 --> 00:57:56.431
Hello. sir. Nice to meet you.

678
00:57:57.932 --> 00:58:00.143
Hi Dad. You like him?

679
00:58:00.977 --> 00:58:03.354
You told me to bring
my boyfriend if I get one.

680
00:58:07.025 --> 00:58:10.487
Mom. what?
He's tall but not good looking?

681
00:58:10.778 --> 00:58:12.113
[Chuckles]

682
00:58:13.781 --> 00:58:18.703
I knew he's a good guy
when I first met him...

683
00:58:19.621 --> 00:58:21.664
as he is a nice person.

684
00:58:37.180 --> 00:58:38.514
It was during Children's Day.

685
00:58:41.059 --> 00:58:43.353
We went for a family trip together.

686
00:58:44.938 --> 00:58:48.149
It was raining but I insisted...

687
00:58:50.610 --> 00:58:55.990
I wanted to do something
before my graduation.

688
00:59:01.955 --> 00:59:04.374
[Dramatic music]

689
00:59:18.805 --> 00:59:20.765
I'm an orphan!

690
00:59:22.392 --> 00:59:23.768
Hey. Open the door!

691
00:59:23.935 --> 00:59:24.602
Who the hell?

692
00:59:24.686 --> 00:59:25.937
[Knocks on door]

693
00:59:28.273 --> 00:59:28.773
What is it?

694
00:59:29.190 --> 00:59:32.819
Police. Someone reported violence.

695
00:59:32.902 --> 00:59:34.612
Open the door! Quick!

696
00:59:34.696 --> 00:59:36.698
Open up!

697
00:59:40.451 --> 00:59:43.079
What the hell are you doing?

698
00:59:43.830 --> 00:59:46.207
Better to die than live like this.

699
00:59:52.171 --> 00:59:54.173
[Sombre music]

700
01:00:43.639 --> 01:00:45.641
[Screams]

701
01:00:50.605 --> 01:00:52.607
[Dramatic music]

702
01:00:55.610 --> 01:00:57.737
I wish they weren't hurt alot...

703
01:01:00.448 --> 01:01:01.657
They would be with me.

704
01:01:06.037 --> 01:01:10.792
They must be watching us together.

705
01:01:12.377 --> 01:01:14.670
I believe they sent you to me.

706
01:01:17.799 --> 01:01:19.801
[Sobbing]

707
01:01:52.208 --> 01:01:52.667
Jung-hwa?

708
01:01:54.752 --> 01:01:56.003
[Gasps]

709
01:02:05.221 --> 01:02:05.888
Is it you?

710
01:02:15.064 --> 01:02:16.816
Sit down. please.

711
01:02:18.234 --> 01:02:21.487
The situatuion of her eyes is critical.

712
01:02:22.155 --> 01:02:25.074
If you leave her like this she'll
lose eyesight forever within a month.

713
01:02:25.950 --> 01:02:29.287
Is there any other way
than waiting for a donor?

714
01:02:30.079 --> 01:02:32.373
Actually. there is...

715
01:02:48.514 --> 01:02:50.516
[Club music]

716
01:02:57.940 --> 01:02:58.608
Here!

717
01:02:58.691 --> 01:03:00.693
[Incoherent chatter]

718
01:03:06.115 --> 01:03:07.992
What brought you here?

719
01:03:10.745 --> 01:03:12.288
I need some money.

720
01:03:13.414 --> 01:03:13.998
How much?

721
01:03:14.540 --> 01:03:15.333
$30.000

722
01:03:17.001 --> 01:03:17.835
By when?

723
01:03:19.545 --> 01:03:20.505
As soon as possible.

724
01:03:23.800 --> 01:03:27.720
Life is full of surprises.

725
01:03:29.639 --> 01:03:31.349
I used to ask you for money.

726
01:03:32.683 --> 01:03:34.685
[Incoherent chatter]

727
01:03:40.441 --> 01:03:41.943
There is one chance.

728
01:03:43.361 --> 01:03:44.570
Do you really need the money?

729
01:03:47.990 --> 01:03:48.658
Wait!

730
01:03:48.699 --> 01:03:49.158
Yes.

731
01:03:52.161 --> 01:03:53.037
Hold on tight.

732
01:03:53.871 --> 01:03:55.873
[Chuckles]

733
01:04:09.220 --> 01:04:09.971
Are you okay?

734
01:04:11.889 --> 01:04:13.266
Why was that?

735
01:04:14.767 --> 01:04:17.562
What took you so long to
take me have this much fun?

736
01:04:20.356 --> 01:04:21.357
Let's get the operation.

737
01:04:21.566 --> 01:04:22.066
What?

738
01:04:23.651 --> 01:04:26.654
Doctor said we can get the cornea.

739
01:04:27.655 --> 01:04:28.656
You knew this. right?

740
01:04:29.824 --> 01:04:30.950
Why didn't you tell me?

741
01:04:33.411 --> 01:04:35.621
The operation is expensive.

742
01:04:36.455 --> 01:04:37.415
Don't worry.

743
01:04:37.957 --> 01:04:38.833
I have some savings.

744
01:04:40.543 --> 01:04:42.753
I like the way we are now.

745
01:04:43.588 --> 01:04:45.256
Having you beside me...

746
01:04:45.965 --> 01:04:47.633
...makes me happier than ever.

747
01:04:48.467 --> 01:04:52.346
It's now or never.

748
01:04:58.978 --> 01:05:04.400
Whenever I think of that day.
and what happened to mom and dad.

749
01:05:06.819 --> 01:05:08.738
I feel guilty and it hurts so bad.

750
01:05:11.490 --> 01:05:12.992
I feel I don't deserve to survive.

751
01:05:15.786 --> 01:05:17.914
I feel better being blind.

752
01:05:23.044 --> 01:05:24.128
Don't want to see me?

753
01:05:25.630 --> 01:05:27.006
How about the babies we'll have?

754
01:05:28.549 --> 01:05:31.510
Don't want to see them?

755
01:05:39.727 --> 01:05:40.394
Married?

756
01:05:41.562 --> 01:05:42.104
No. sir.

757
01:05:44.065 --> 01:05:44.774
Girlfriend?

758
01:05:47.109 --> 01:05:47.652
Yes.

759
01:05:48.819 --> 01:05:52.907
This fight can be really dangerous...

760
01:05:53.199 --> 01:05:54.492
Are you okay with that?

761
01:05:55.076 --> 01:05:56.035
I won't fail.

762
01:05:57.119 --> 01:05:58.663
$30.000 for advance.

763
01:05:58.788 --> 01:06:00.164
Rest after the work is done.

764
01:06:00.289 --> 01:06:02.416
A duplicate phone for you.

765
01:06:04.877 --> 01:06:11.550
This money is nothing
but for an ordinary fight.

766
01:06:12.385 --> 01:06:15.554
But when Thai police finds out.

767
01:06:16.013 --> 01:06:17.723
it gets complicated.

768
01:06:19.517 --> 01:06:24.230
Nobody can help you if
you get caught. understand?

769
01:06:24.730 --> 01:06:25.481
Say. yes.

770
01:06:32.446 --> 01:06:33.698
You're not answering?

771
01:06:36.033 --> 01:06:36.617
I get it.

772
01:06:37.451 --> 01:06:39.453
[Dramatic music]

773
01:06:49.505 --> 01:06:54.176
-Take good care of her.
-[Dog barks]

774
01:07:00.891 --> 01:07:02.893
Practice vigilance.

775
01:07:04.437 --> 01:07:07.231
Your family can get hurt.

776
01:07:07.982 --> 01:07:11.485
So be sure that nobody can track you.

777
01:07:12.528 --> 01:07:14.071
That can increase trouble.

778
01:07:20.119 --> 01:07:21.537
Are you crazy?

779
01:07:21.996 --> 01:07:23.622
Told you not to deal with Tae-sik.

780
01:07:23.914 --> 01:07:26.000
Don't know what you're doing.

781
01:07:26.584 --> 01:07:28.252
It's only one fight.

782
01:07:28.502 --> 01:07:32.673
We finally got into the official
league after all these sufferings!

783
01:07:33.174 --> 01:07:36.385
Is this for her eyes?

784
01:07:39.305 --> 01:07:43.517
If something happens.
...balance will be wired.

785
01:07:44.101 --> 01:07:45.811
Please give it to her. okay?

786
01:07:48.773 --> 01:07:50.941
What if you become crippled?

787
01:07:52.735 --> 01:07:54.445
You've got only one life to live!

788
01:07:55.654 --> 01:07:57.114
I won't regret it.

789
01:08:12.421 --> 01:08:14.006
You're absolutely right.

790
01:08:15.633 --> 01:08:16.342
About what?

791
01:08:17.968 --> 01:08:24.558
I want to see the sunset
with you. also lovely Easy.

792
01:08:25.059 --> 01:08:29.730
...our house you fixed.

793
01:08:30.356 --> 01:08:32.024
river we went together.

794
01:08:32.274 --> 01:08:33.359
And...

795
01:08:34.735 --> 01:08:35.736
And?

796
01:08:37.947 --> 01:08:42.493
I'll lie on my bed and
see your face only.

797
01:08:43.452 --> 01:08:47.456
I'll work for 23 hours but one
hour is reserved only for your face.

798
01:08:48.874 --> 01:08:53.838
What if you look a
lot uglier than I think?

799
01:08:54.922 --> 01:08:56.465
What will I do then?

800
01:08:56.674 --> 01:08:59.260
[Chuckles]

801
01:09:00.553 --> 01:09:04.056
You'd better get prepared
for looking at me closely.

802
01:09:06.183 --> 01:09:07.560
I look really bad.

803
01:09:08.811 --> 01:09:10.229
You might not recognize me.

804
01:09:10.938 --> 01:09:12.773
This will never be.

805
01:09:17.444 --> 01:09:18.696
I'm so nervous.

806
01:09:22.658 --> 01:09:24.660
[Pleasant music]

807
01:09:33.294 --> 01:09:34.837
I'll see you soon!

808
01:09:38.591 --> 01:09:39.550
I want that too.

809
01:09:40.718 --> 01:09:42.720
[Pleasant music]

810
01:09:54.940 --> 01:09:56.442
Wait for me here.

811
01:09:57.276 --> 01:09:58.527
Don't go anywhere.

812
01:10:01.614 --> 01:10:04.199
I've got no place to go but you.

813
01:10:06.160 --> 01:10:07.036
See you soon.

814
01:10:10.080 --> 01:10:12.082
[Pleasant music]

815
01:10:35.314 --> 01:10:37.316
[Dramatic music]

816
01:10:43.155 --> 01:10:44.782
Memorize your name and address.

817
01:10:45.532 --> 01:10:47.618
From now on. you are Kim Hak-sun.

818
01:10:48.369 --> 01:10:50.746
We won't all have your number.

819
01:10:51.914 --> 01:10:57.461
No relative. no conviction.
the police is not chasing you.

820
01:10:59.296 --> 01:11:01.256
[Dramatic music]

821
01:11:17.815 --> 01:11:19.817
[Incoherent chatter]

822
01:11:35.749 --> 01:11:36.292
[Opens door]

823
01:11:56.729 --> 01:11:57.938
[Closes door]

824
01:12:03.944 --> 01:12:07.197
Never saw you get nervous like this.

825
01:12:09.491 --> 01:12:11.869
This man has already put many into death.

826
01:12:13.203 --> 01:12:14.788
Don't even try to win.

827
01:12:15.039 --> 01:12:16.457
Try to survive.

828
01:12:23.047 --> 01:12:24.548
There's no rule.

829
01:12:24.840 --> 01:12:28.844
Game ends only when
one dies or passes out.

830
01:12:53.952 --> 01:12:57.539
Want to know whom I bet on?

831
01:12:59.166 --> 01:13:01.377
Sweat it out. Doggy.

832
01:13:11.428 --> 01:13:13.430
[Dramatic music]

833
01:13:17.643 --> 01:13:18.894
[Locking door]

834
01:13:19.061 --> 01:13:21.063
[Dramatic music]

835
01:13:53.929 --> 01:13:55.931
[Incoherent chatter]

836
01:13:57.516 --> 01:13:59.268
He won't last.

837
01:14:00.394 --> 01:14:00.978
Let's go.

838
01:14:01.019 --> 01:14:03.021
[Incoherent cheering]

839
01:14:04.648 --> 01:14:05.149
Very good!

840
01:14:13.448 --> 01:14:15.826
Very good! Come on! Come on!

841
01:14:15.826 --> 01:14:18.036
Finish this match quickly!

842
01:14:18.579 --> 01:14:21.748
